<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 03 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近啊，<delay20 /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />经常开着电视<delay8 />
当做背景音乐，
但是都没有仔细在看<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你呢？<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一天大概看几个小时电视啊？</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="02 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不到一小时吧。</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="03 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好像不怎么看</message>
	<message label="001_c" attrib="04 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一整天都在看哦！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />原来如此。<delay20 />
所以你只看想看的节目咯。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实我啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对那种有动物和小孩子登场的节目<delay8 />
完全没有抵抗力<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次看到那种催人泪下的节目，<delay8 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就一下子上钩了，<delay20 />
所以只有独自一人的时候才会看。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦？<delay8 />这样啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近好像<delay8 />
还挺多人不看电视的嘛。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />兴趣和爱好也越来越多样化了，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也许这就是时代的潮流吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样啊～<delay20 />也就是说
你是个忠实的电视观众咯？！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过这样一来，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不就没有时间<delay8 />
去钓鱼或者捕虫之类的了吗？！
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />凡事都要适可而止哦！<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="07 00 00 01 00 00 00 09">说起来，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有什么不喜欢的东西吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay20 />大部分东西
都不太介意，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唯独医院实在是不太习惯。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x8 0x9 0xa" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说到医院，<delay8 />
最先联想到的就是打针对吧？！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次打针的时候<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都跟你说<delay8 />“不痛的哦～”，<delay40 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果根本是骗人的！
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不行不行！<delay20 />
我绝对不要打针！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">说到医院，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总是会联想到那独特的味道对吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是那种充满候诊室的，<delay8 />
不知道是消毒液还是什么的刺鼻气味啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总感觉，
连我自己都要和细菌一起被消毒掉了，<delay20 />
实在很不习惯<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />小的时候，<delay8 />又是受伤啊、<delay8 />
又是发烧的，<delay8 /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />父母经常带我去医院。
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过最近这阵子为了进行健康检查，<delay8 />
我也经常往医院跑。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从以前开始，<delay8 />我就不太喜欢检查啦、<delay8 />考试啦<delay20 />
这类事情。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="0d 00 00 01 00 00 00 09">别看我现在圆滑了不少，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />曾经有一段时间，<delay8 />
我可是<delay8 />相当自以为是啊。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xe 0xf 0x10" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">比如说鞋子。<delay8 />当时，<delay8 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我总是穿着那种<delay8 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鞋头尖到不行的鞋子<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />爬楼梯<delay8 />的时候，
实在是麻烦到不行啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">比如说裤子。<delay8 />当时，<delay8 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我总是穿着那种<delay8 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />简直可以叫作裤裙的宽松裤子<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一次我把两只脚穿进了一条裤腿里，<delay20 />
偏偏当时还在赶路，<delay8 />
结果只能用小跑的。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">比如说自行车。<delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当时我把坐垫压得很低，<delay8 />
车把手反而提得很高，<delay20 />
扭着身子骑在上面<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />手又酸、<delay8 />又难踩，<delay20 />
还不如走路来得轻松呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="13 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刚才我突然想起了<delay8 />
小时候玩的一些游戏。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x14 0x15 0x16" /></message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那时候，<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />不是会玩捉迷藏吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay8 />好像几乎从来没扮过鬼，<delay20 />
而且每次都是最后被找到。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一直觉得很奇怪，<delay20 />
到后来才了解到其中的缘由<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说是<delay8 />如果我扮鬼那就真的太可怕了，<delay20 />
所以他们特别规定<delay20 />
我不能扮鬼！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那时候，<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />不是会玩过家家吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay8 /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次都扮演<delay20 />
被妈妈念叨的爸爸。
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实我很想<delay20 />
扮演一次宝宝，<delay8 />
让妈妈摸摸我的头呢！</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那时候，<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />不是会玩跳大绳吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay8 />一下子就会绊到绳子，<delay20 />
所以每次都只能负责甩绳子。
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />甩啊、<delay20 />甩啊、<delay8 />
甩个不停，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果导致我现在变成平肩了！</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="1b 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay20 />实在是不太上镜。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要怎么样才能，怎么说<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
拍出<delay8 />别人看着舒服的照片呢？</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次镜头一对准我，<delay20 />
我就会<delay8 />特别紧张，<delay20 />
变成好像在瞪别人一样。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />干脆啊，<delay20 />
拍下我和你说话时候的样子。<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说不定能拍出看着舒服的照片啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">虽然常听别人说什么自然一点的动作<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但从根本上来说，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />摆造型这个行为<delay20 />本身<delay8 />就不自然嘛！
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="60" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还是觉得<delay20 />双手抱胸，<delay8 />
眼神凶狠一点看起来比较威猛，<delay20 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉不错啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0x19 0x1a" /></message>
</msbt>